[" Fast Dynamic Time Warping\n\nThis is an approximate solution to dynamic time warping.\n\nParameters\n----------\nX : np.ndarray\n    Array X.\nY: np.ndarray\n    Array Y.\nmetric : str\n    The name of the metric to use. See possible metrics in\n    `scipy.spatial.distance`.\n\nReturns\n-------\nwarping_path: np.ndarray\n    The warping path for the best alignment. The first column\n    are indices in array `X` and the second column represents\n    the corresponding index in array `Y`.\ndtwd : float\n    The dynamic time warping distance of the alignment."]}, {"name": "mpteval.util.greedy_note_alignment", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "warping_path", "type": {"name": "np.ndarray", "xref": {"fqname": "numpy.ndarray", "project": "numpy"}, "params": null}, "default": null}, {"name": "idx1", "type": {"name": "np.ndarray", "xref": {"fqname": "numpy.ndarray", "project": "numpy"}, "params": null}, "default": null}, {"name": "note_array1", "type": {"name": "np.ndarray", "xref": {"fqname": "numpy.ndarray", "project": "numpy"}, "params": null}, "default": null}, {"name": "idx2", "type": {"name": "np.ndarray", "xref": {"fqname": "numpy.ndarray", "project": "numpy"}, "params": null}, "default": null}, {"name": "note_array2", "type": {"name": "np.ndarray", "xref": {"fqname": "numpy.ndarray", "project": "numpy"}, "params": null}, "default": null}], "returns": {"name": "List", "xref": {"fqname": "typing.List", "project": "--std--"}, "params": [{"name": "dict", "xref": {"fqname": "functions.dict", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}]}, "documentation": ["Greedily find and store possible note alignments\n\nParameters\n----------\nwarping_path : numpy ndarray\n    alignment sequence idx in stacked columns\nidx1: numpy ndarray\n    pitch, start, and end coordinates of all notes in note_array1\nnote_array1: numpy structured array\n    note_array of sequence 1 (the score)\nidx2: numpy ndarray\n    pitch, start, and end coordinates of all notes in note_array2\nnote_array2: numpy structured array\n    note_array of sequence 2 (the performance)\n\nReturns\n----------\nnote_alignment : list\n    list of note alignment dictionaries"]}, {"name": "mpteval.util.notewise_alignment", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "reference_features", "type": {"name": "np.ndarray", "xref": {"fqname": "numpy.ndarray", "project": "numpy"}, "params": null}, "default": null}, {"name": "performance_features", "type": {"name": "np.ndarray", "xref": {"fqname": "numpy.ndarray", "project": "numpy"}, "params": null}, "default": null}, {"name": "score_note_array", "type": {"name": "np.ndarray", "xref": {"fqname": "numpy.ndarray", "project": "numpy"}, "params": null}, "default": null}, {"name": "performance_note_array", "type": {"name": "np.ndarray", "xref": {"fqname": "numpy.ndarray", "project": "numpy"}, "params": null}, "default": null}, {"name": "sidx", "type": {"name": "np.ndarray", "xref": {"fqname": "numpy.ndarray", "project": "numpy"}, "params": null}, "default": null}, {"name": "pidx", "type": {"name": "np.ndarray", "xref": {"fqname": "numpy.ndarray", "project": "numpy"}, "params": null}, "default": null}, {"name": "metric", "type": {"name": "str", "xref": {"fqname": "functions.str", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, "default": "..."}], "returns": {"name": "List", "xref": {"fqname": "typing.List", "project": "--std--"}, "params": [{"name": "dict", "xref": {"fqname": "functions.dict", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}]}, "documentation": ["Note-wise music alignment\n\nParameters\n-----------\nreference_features : np.ndarray\n    Features of the reference (usually the score). Usually\n    a piano roll or pitch class distribution\nperformance_features: np.ndarray\n    Features of the performance.\nsidx : np.ndarray\n    Indices of the notes in the reference_features\npidx : np.ndarray\n    Indices of the notes in the performance_features\nmetric : str\n    Local metric for on-line time warping\n\nReturns\n-------\nnote_alignment : List[dict]\n    List with alignment information for each note in\n    the score and the performance."]}], "variables": [], "classes": [], "exports": []}, {"name": "mpteval.timing", "documentation": ["Timing metrics for transcription:\n- IOI correlation for melody and accompaniment streams\n- DTW distance between IOI sequences for melody and accompaniment streams\n- Kullback-Leibler divergence between IOI histograms for melody and accompaniment streams"], "functions": [{"name": "mpteval.timing.compute_ioi_stream", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "note_array", "type": {"name": "np.ndarray", "xref": {"fqname": "numpy.ndarray", "project": "numpy"}, "params": null}, "default": null}], "returns": {"name": "np.ndarray", "xref": {"fqname": "numpy.ndarray", "project": "numpy"}, "params": null}, "documentation": []}, {"name": "mpteval.timing.get_ioi_stream_func", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "note_array", "type": {"name": "np.ndarray", "xref": {"fqname": "numpy.ndarray", "project": "numpy"}, "params": null}, "default": null}], "returns": {"name": "Callable", "xref": {"fqname": "typing.Callable", "project": "--std--"}, "params": [{"name": "", "xref": null, "params": [{"name": "np.ndarray", "xref": {"fqname": "numpy.ndarray", "project": "numpy"}, "params": null}]}, {"name": "np.ndarray", "xref": {"fqname": "numpy.ndarray", "project": "numpy"}, "params": null}]}, "documentation": []}, {"name": "mpteval.timing.timing_metrics_from_perf", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "ref_perf", "type": {"name": "Union", "xref": {"fqname": "typing.Union", "project": "--std--"}, "params": [{"name": "PerformedPart", "xref": {"fqname": "partitura.performance.PerformedPart", "project": "partitura"}, "params": null}, {"name": "Performance", "xref": {"fqname": "partitura.performance.Performance", "project": "partitura"}, "params": null}]}, "default": null}, {"name": "pred_perf", "type": {"name": "Union", "xref": {"fqname": "typing.Union", "project": "--std--"}, "params": [{"name": "PerformedPart", "xref": {"fqname": "partitura.performance.PerformedPart", "project": "partitura"}, "params": null}, {"name": "Performance", "xref": {"fqname": "partitura.performance.Performance", "project": "partitura"}, "params": null}]}, "default": null}], "returns": {"name": "np.ndarray", "xref": {"fqname": "numpy.ndarray", "project": "numpy"}, "params": null}, "documentation": []}], "variables": [], "classes": [], "exports": []}, {"name": "mpteval.harmony", "documentation": ["Harmony metrics for transcription"], "functions": [{"name": "mpteval.harmony.get_tonal_tension_feature_func", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "note_array", "type": {"name": "np.ndarray", "xref": {"fqname": "numpy.ndarray", "project": "numpy"}, "params": null}, "default": null}, {"name": "feature", "type": {"name": "str", "xref": {"fqname": "functions.str", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, "default": null}, {"name": "ws", "type": {"name": "int", "xref": {"fqname": "functions.int", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, "default": null}, {"name": "ss", "type": {"name": "int", "xref": {"fqname": "functions.int", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, "default": null}, {"name": "return_onsets", "type": {"name": "bool", "xref": {"fqname": "functions.bool", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, "default": "..."}], "returns": {"name": "Tuple", "xref": {"fqname": "typing.Tuple", "project": "--std--"}, "params": [{"name": "np.ndarray", "xref": {"fqname": "numpy.ndarray", "project": "numpy"}, "params": null}, {"name": "Callable", "xref": {"fqname": "typing.Callable", "project": "--std--"}, "params": [{"name": "", "xref": null, "params": [{"name": "np.ndarray", "xref": {"fqname": "numpy.ndarray", "project": "numpy"}, "params": null}]}, {"name": "np.ndarray", "xref": {"fqname": "numpy.ndarray", "project": "numpy"}, "params": null}]}]}, "documentation": ["Compute a tonal tension feature and return the interpolation function for that feature.\n\n# Parameters\n\nnote_array\n\n: Note array for the stream\n\nfeature\n\n: The tonal tension feature to compute. One of 'cloud_diameter', 'cloud_momentum', 'tensile_strain' (see [^footnote-1]).\n\nws\n\n: Window size for tonal tension estimation\n\nss\n\n: Step size for tonal tension estimation\n\n# Returns\n\ntonal_tension[feature]\n\n: Array containing the tonal tension feature values.\n\nfeat_func : Callable\\[[np.ndarray], np.ndarray\\]\n\n# References\n\n[^footnote-1]: D. Herremans and E. Chew (2016) Tension ribbons: Quantifying and\n    visualising tonal tension. Proceedings of the Second International\n    Conference on Technologies for Music Notation and Representation\n    (TENOR), Cambridge, UK.\n"]}, {"name": "mpteval.harmony.harmony_metrics_from_perf", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "ref_perf", "type": {"name": "PerformedPart", "xref": {"fqname": "partitura.performance.PerformedPart", "project": "partitura"}, "params": null}, "default": null}, {"name": "pred_perf", "type": {"name": "PerformedPart", "xref": {"fqname": "partitura.performance.PerformedPart", "project": "partitura"}, "params": null}, "default": null}, {"name": "ws", "type": null, "default": "..."}, {"name": "ss", "type": null, "default": "..."}], "returns": {"name": "np.ndarray", "xref": {"fqname": "numpy.ndarray", "project": "numpy"}, "params": null}, "documentation": ["Compute the correlation between the tonal tension of the ground truth and predicted performances.\n\nSpecifically, we compute the correlation between the following measures of tonal tension:\n- cloud diameter\n- cloud momentum\n- tensile strain"]}], "variables": [], "classes": [], "exports": []}, {"name": "mpteval.articulation", "documentation": ["Articulation-based metrics for transcription"], "functions": [{"name": "mpteval.articulation.chordify_perf_note_array", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "note_array", "type": {"name": "np.ndarray", "xref": {"fqname": "numpy.ndarray", "project": "numpy"}, "params": null}, "default": null}, {"name": "ioi_threshold", "type": {"name": "float", "xref": {"fqname": "functions.float", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, "default": "..."}, {"name": "max_threshold", "type": {"name": "float", "xref": {"fqname": "functions.float", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, "default": "..."}], "returns": {"name": "List", "xref": {"fqname": "typing.List", "project": "--std--"}, "params": [{"name": "PerformedChord", "xref": {"fqname": "mpteval.articulation.dynamics.PerformedChord", "project": null}, "params": null}]}, "documentation": ["Chordify a performance note array.\n\nParameters\n----------\nnote_array : np.ndarray\n    An input note array\nioi_threshold : float, optional\n    Maximal Inter-onset interval between notes in the chord,\n    in seconds, by default 0.03\nmax_threshold : float, optional\n    Maximal value between the onset time of the first\n    and last note in the chord, by default 0.05\n\nReturns\n-------\nchords : List[PerformedChord]\n    List of performed chords."]}, {"name": "mpteval.articulation.skyline_melody_identification_from_array", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "note_array", "type": {"name": "np.ndarray", "xref": {"fqname": "numpy.ndarray", "project": "numpy"}, "params": null}, "default": null}], "returns": {"name": "Tuple", "xref": {"fqname": "typing.Tuple", "project": "--std--"}, "params": [{"name": "np.ndarray", "xref": {"fqname": "numpy.ndarray", "project": "numpy"}, "params": null}, {"name": "np.ndarray", "xref": {"fqname": "numpy.ndarray", "project": "numpy"}, "params": null}]}, "documentation": ["Main melody line identification using the skyline algorithm.\n\nThe skyline algorithm was first proposed by Uitdenbogerd and Zobel [1]_\nand has seen various implementations. The implementation referenced\nhere is adapted from Simonetta et al. [2]_.\n\nParameters\n----------\nnote_array : np.ndarray\n    Input note array (from a PerformedPart or Part).\n\nReturns\n-------\nmelody_line : np.ndarray\n    A note array corresponding to the notes in the melody.\n\naccompaniment : np.ndarray:\n    A note array corresponding to the notes in the accompaniment\n    (i.e., everything that is not in the main melody line)\n\nReferences\n  ----------\n  .. [1] A. L. Uitdenbogerd and J. Zobel, \"Melodic matching techniques for\n     large music databases,\" in Proceedings of the 7th ACM International\n     Conference on Multimedia '99, Orlando, FL, USA, October 30 - November 5,\n     1999, Part 1, pp. 57-66.\n\n  .. [2] F. Simonetta, C. Cancino-Chac\u00f3n, S. Ntalampiras and G. Widmer \"A Convolutional\n     Approach to Melody Line Identification in Symbolic Scores,\" in Proceedings of the\n     20th International Society for Music Information Retrieval Conference (ISMIR 2019),\n     Delft, The Netherlands."]}, {"name": "mpteval.articulation.skyline_melody_identification", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "note_array", "type": {"name": "np.ndarray", "xref": {"fqname": "numpy.ndarray", "project": "numpy"}, "params": null}, "default": null}, {"name": "staff_threshold", "type": null, "default": "..."}, {"name": "ioi_threshold", "type": {"name": "float", "xref": {"fqname": "functions.float", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, "default": "..."}, {"name": "max_threshold", "type": {"name": "float", "xref": {"fqname": "functions.float", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, "default": "..."}], "returns": {"name": "Tuple", "xref": {"fqname": "typing.Tuple", "project": "--std--"}, "params": [{"name": "np.ndarray", "xref": {"fqname": "numpy.ndarray", "project": "numpy"}, "params": null}, {"name": "np.ndarray", "xref": {"fqname": "numpy.ndarray", "project": "numpy"}, "params": null}, {"name": "np.ndarray", "xref": {"fqname": "numpy.ndarray", "project": "numpy"}, "params": null}]}, "documentation": []}, {"name": "mpteval.articulation.compute_kor_stream", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "note_array", "type": {"name": "np.ndarray", "xref": {"fqname": "numpy.ndarray", "project": "